### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

### Single Prediction - Setosa
POST http://localhost:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "features": {
        "sepal_length": 5.1,
        "sepal_width": 3.5,
        "petal_length": 1.4,
        "petal_width": 0.2
    }
}

### Single Prediction - Versicolor
POST http://localhost:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "features": {
        "sepal_length": 6.5,
        "sepal_width": 2.8,
        "petal_length": 4.6,
        "petal_width": 1.5
    }
}

### Single Prediction - Virginica
POST http://localhost:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "features": {
        "sepal_length": 6.3,
        "sepal_width": 3.3,
        "petal_length": 6.0,
        "petal_width": 2.5
    }
}

### Batch Prediction
POST http://localhost:8000/predict_batch
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "features": {
            "sepal_length": 5.1,
            "sepal_width": 3.5,
            "petal_length": 1.4,
            "petal_width": 0.2
        }
    },
    {
        "features": {
            "sepal_length": 6.5,
            "sepal_width": 2.8,
            "petal_length": 4.6,
            "petal_width": 1.5
        }
    },
    {
        "features": {
            "sepal_length": 6.3,
            "sepal_width": 3.3,
            "petal_length": 6.0,
            "petal_width": 2.5
        }
    }
]
